* Mouse wheel for list scrolling or map zooming
* Bridge upgrades: Build a new bridge over the old bridge to upgrade it. You can't change the type, e.g. road to rail, this way. If upgrading a town bridge the new bridge must have a higher top speed, but otherwise it can be anything you like. (0.6.0)
